<p class="eyebrow">Voice Calling</p>
<h1>Wholesale voice for managed service providers, carriers, and operators.</h1>
<p class="lede">Intelligent routing directs traffic to the nearest or most optimal node using Anycast, or to nodes within a specific geographic area with Geocast, ensuring fast, localized delivery. Diverse path routing enhances reliability by automatically switching among multiple network paths or carriers to avoid failures and congestion. Together, these techniques support business continuity by maximizing performance, resilience, and uninterrupted delivery of critical services.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/pricing/">See pricing</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/voiceml/">Explore VoiceML</a>
</p>

